<paragraph id="16B328410A1EEB0FE5C1A99AE99AD006" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">Male holotype (AP645) from Arizona, Cochise County, Portal, 31.91369, -109.1408 1, 1450m, coll. S. Bennett 12.ix.1980; deposited in AMNH.</paragraph>
